snippet.title: Paint the Town Red - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Paint the Town Red is now available on the PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch and Steam (Windows, Mac and Linux).

Buy the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/337320/Paint_the_Town_Red/
Or buy it on your console's store

Twitter – https://twitter.com/southeastgames
Website - https://www.southeastgames.com
